    {
      "id": "post-1780663113659",
      "title": "Fail Safe Logic",
      "author": "Admin",
      "date": "2026-06-05",
      "category": "General",
      "tags": [
        "Fail Safe"
      ],
      "coverImage": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/Fail%20Safe.jpeg",
      "excerpt": "Fail Safe Logic in each project often not goes to advance level.",
      "content": "<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p> In almost all the project, fail safe design and logic is given less importance and carried out only for customer satisfaction.\nAny Fail Safe logic must have details like which Safety Category has been adopted, how it is designed and how it is going to be executed. \nCustomer will be more curious and will realize how serious are we about safety.\nWiring E-Stop to safety relay or PLC often goes with theory logic.\nThis must be analyzed in detail, designer need to adopt a system to understand what type of safety ,customer requires or if he is not aware, based on project 3D CAD needs to present safety category adopted in design.\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/Fail%20Safe.jpeg\" \n     style=\"width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:12px 0;\" />",
      "isPinned": true,
      "isPublished": true,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-05T12:38:33.659Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "post-1782194326819",
      "title": "Controls Project Allocation & Assignment",
      "author": "Admin",
      "date": "2026-06-23",
      "category": "General",
      "tags": [
        "#Project_Assignment_Matrix"
      ],
      "coverImage": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/project-template.jpg",
      "excerpt": "Dynamic project allocation template with engineer selection from GitHub. Assign team members, dates, and tasks. Download filled forms for approval and signatures",
      "content": "<!-- CONTROLS PROJECT FORM - FINAL WORKING VERSION -->\n<style>\n.cpf-container{max-width:900px;margin:20px auto;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:#fff;padding:20px;border:1px solid #ddd}\n.cpf-header{background:#667eea;color:#fff;padding:20px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:25px}\n.cpf-header h2{margin:0;font-size:22px}\n.cpf-header p{margin:5px 0 0 0;font-size:12px}\n.cpf-section{background:#f9f9f9;border-left:4px solid #667eea;padding:15px;margin-bottom:15px;border-radius:4px}\n.cpf-section h3{color:#003366;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;padding-bottom:5px}\n.cpf-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px}\n.cpf-grid.full{grid-template-columns:1fr}\n.cpf-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column}\n.cpf-group label{font-size:11px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;color:#555}\n.cpf-group input,.cpf-group select{padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%}\n.cpf-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:10px 0;font-size:10px}\n.cpf-table th{background:#e8e8e8;padding:8px;text-align:left;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd}\n.cpf-table td{padding:6px;border:1px solid #ddd}\n.cpf-table input{width:100%;padding:4px;border:1px solid #ddd;box-sizing:border-box}\n.cpf-checkbox-group{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin:8px 0}\n.cpf-checkbox-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:11px}\n.cpf-checkbox-item input{width:14px;height:14px}\n.cpf-buttons{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:20px 0;justify-content:center}\n.cpf-btn{padding:12px 24px;border:none;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px}\n.cpf-btn-save{background:#4caf50;color:#fff}\n.cpf-btn-save:hover{background:#45a049}\n.cpf-btn-pdf{background:#2196f3;color:#fff}\n.cpf-btn-pdf:hover{background:#0b7dda}\n.cpf-btn-reset{background:#f0f0f0;color:#666;border:1px solid #ccc}\n.cpf-status{padding:12px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;display:none;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid}\n.cpf-status.success{background:#d4edda;color:#155724;border-color:#c3e6cb}\n.cpf-status.error{background:#f8d7da;color:#721c24;border-color:#f5c6cb}\n.cpf-status.show{display:block}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"cpf-container\" id=\"cpfMain\">\n  <div class=\"cpf-header\">\n    <h2>⚙️ Controls Project Allocation & Assignment</h2>\n    <p>Fill form and save or download</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <form id=\"cpfForm\">\n    \n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>1. Project Overview</h3>\n      <div class=\"cpf-grid\">\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Project Name</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"cpfProjectName\" name=\"cpfProjectName\" placeholder=\"Name\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Project Code</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"cpfProjectCode\" name=\"cpfProjectCode\" placeholder=\"Code\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Client/Facility</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"cpfClient\" name=\"cpfClient\" placeholder=\"Client\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Project Manager</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"cpfProjectManager\" name=\"cpfProjectManager\" placeholder=\"PM\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Start Date</label>\n          <input type=\"date\" id=\"cpfStartDate\" name=\"cpfStartDate\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Completion Date</label>\n          <input type=\"date\" id=\"cpfCompletionDate\" name=\"cpfCompletionDate\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Budget</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"cpfBudget\" name=\"cpfBudget\" placeholder=\"Amount\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Priority</label>\n          <select id=\"cpfPriority\" name=\"cpfPriority\">\n            <option>Select</option>\n            <option>Critical</option>\n            <option>High</option>\n            <option>Medium</option>\n            <option>Low</option>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>2. Project Scope & Systems</h3>\n      <label style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:11px\">Automation Systems</label>\n      <div class=\"cpf-checkbox-group\">\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cpfSystems\"> PLC Programming</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cpfSystems\"> HMI/SCADA</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cpfSystems\"> Motor Control</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cpfSystems\"> Instrumentation</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cpfSystems\"> Industrial Networks</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"cpfSystems\"> Safety Systems</label>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>3. Team Assignment Matrix</h3>\n      <table class=\"cpf-table\">\n        <tr><th>Team Member</th><th>Role</th><th>Tasks</th><th>Hours</th><th>Start</th><th>End</th></tr>\n        <tr><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"number\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td></tr>\n        <tr><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"number\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td></tr>\n        <tr><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"number\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>4. Skill Requirements & Certifications</h3>\n      <table class=\"cpf-table\">\n        <tr><th>Certification</th><th>Team Member</th><th>Status</th></tr>\n        <tr><td>PLC Programming</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n        <tr><td>HMI Development</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Industrial Safety</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Electrical Installation</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>8. Risk Assessment & Mitigation</h3>\n      <table class=\"cpf-table\">\n        <tr><th>Risk Factor</th><th>Probability</th><th>Impact</th><th>Mitigation</th></tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Equipment Delivery Delays</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Site Access Restrictions</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Technical Skill Gaps</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Safety Incidents</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>Document Information</h3>\n      <div class=\"cpf-grid\">\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Prepared By</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"cpfPreparedBy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Approved By</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"cpfApprovedBy\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-buttons\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"cpf-btn cpf-btn-save\" id=\"cpfBtnSave\">💾 Save Locally</button>\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"cpf-btn cpf-btn-pdf\" id=\"cpfBtnPdf\">📥 Download PDF</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" class=\"cpf-btn cpf-btn-reset\">🔄 Reset</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"cpfStatus\" class=\"cpf-status\"></div>\n  </form>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n// REGISTER FUNCTIONS IN GLOBAL SCOPE IMMEDIATELY\nwindow.cpfShowStatus = function(msg, type) {\n  var status = document.getElementById('cpfStatus');\n  if (status) {\n    status.textContent = msg;\n    status.className = 'cpf-status ' + type + ' show';\n    setTimeout(function() {\n      status.className = 'cpf-status';\n    }, 4000);\n  }\n};\n\nwindow.cpfSaveForm = function() {\n  try {\n    var projectCode = (document.getElementById('cpfProjectCode') || {}).value || 'Project';\n    var projectName = (document.getElementById('cpfProjectName') || {}).value || 'Unnamed';\n\n    if (!projectCode.trim()) {\n      window.cpfShowStatus('❌ Please enter Project Code', 'error');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    var formData = {};\n    var form = document.getElementById('cpfForm');\n    if (form) {\n      var inputs = form.querySelectorAll('input, select, textarea');\n      inputs.forEach(function(field) {\n        var key = field.id || field.name || 'field_' + Math.random();\n        if (field.type === 'checkbox' || field.type === 'radio') {\n          formData[key] = field.checked;\n        } else {\n          formData[key] = field.value;\n        }\n      });\n    }\n\n    var data = {\n      projectCode: projectCode,\n      projectName: projectName,\n      timestamp: new Date().toLocaleString(),\n      formData: formData\n    };\n\n    var storageKey = 'cpf_' + projectCode.replace(/\\s+/g, '_') + '_' + Date.now();\n    localStorage.setItem(storageKey, JSON.stringify(data));\n    localStorage.setItem('cpf_latest_' + projectCode.replace(/\\s+/g, '_'), JSON.stringify(data));\n\n    window.cpfShowStatus('✅ Saved: ' + projectName + ' (' + projectCode + ')', 'success');\n  } catch (error) {\n    window.cpfShowStatus('❌ Error: ' + error.message, 'error');\n  }\n};\n\nwindow.cpfGeneratePDF = function() {\n  try {\n    var projectCode = (document.getElementById('cpfProjectCode') || {}).value || 'Project';\n    var projectName = (document.getElementById('cpfProjectName') || {}).value || 'Unnamed';\n\n    if (!projectCode.trim()) {\n      window.cpfShowStatus('❌ Please enter Project Code', 'error');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    var title = projectCode + ' - ' + projectName;\n    var date = new Date().toLocaleDateString();\n    var mainDiv = document.getElementById('cpfMain');\n    var content = mainDiv ? mainDiv.innerHTML : '';\n\n    var htmlContent = '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><title>' + title + '</title><style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;margin:20px;color:#333}h1{color:#667eea;border-bottom:3px solid #667eea;padding-bottom:10px;margin-bottom:5px}h2{color:#003366;margin-top:20px;font-size:14px}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:10px 0;font-size:11px}th,td{border:1px solid #ddd;padding:8px;text-align:left}th{background:#f0f0f0;font-weight:bold}.cpf-section{page-break-inside:avoid;margin-bottom:15px}@media print{body{margin:0}}</style></head><body><h1>' + title + '</h1><p><strong>Date:</strong> ' + date + '</p>' + content + '<p style=\"margin-top:40px;border-top:1px solid #ddd;padding-top:20px;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Generated on: ' + new Date().toLocaleString() + '</p></body></html>';\n\n    var blob = new Blob([htmlContent], { type: 'text/html' });\n    var url = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob);\n    var link = document.createElement('a');\n    link.href = url;\n    link.download = projectCode.replace(/\\s+/g, '_') + '_' + date.replace(/\\//g, '-') + '.html';\n    \n    document.body.appendChild(link);\n    link.click();\n    document.body.removeChild(link);\n    window.URL.revokeObjectURL(url);\n\n    window.cpfShowStatus('✅ HTML file downloaded. Open in browser and use Print → Save as PDF', 'success');\n  } catch (error) {\n    window.cpfShowStatus('❌ Error: ' + error.message, 'error');\n  }\n};\n\n// ATTACH EVENT LISTENERS WHEN DOM IS READY\nif (document.readyState === 'loading') {\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n    var btnSave = document.getElementById('cpfBtnSave');\n    var btnPdf = document.getElementById('cpfBtnPdf');\n    if (btnSave) btnSave.addEventListener('click', window.cpfSaveForm);\n    if (btnPdf) btnPdf.addEventListener('click', window.cpfGeneratePDF);\n  });\n} else {\n  var btnSave = document.getElementById('cpfBtnSave');\n  var btnPdf = document.getElementById('cpfBtnPdf');\n  if (btnSave) btnSave.addEventListener('click', window.cpfSaveForm);\n  if (btnPdf) btnPdf.addEventListener('click', window.cpfGeneratePDF);\n}\n\nconsole.log('CPF Form Initialized Successfully');\n</script>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "isPublished": true,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-23T05:58:46.819Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "post-1782029100720",
      "title": "Material BOM Tracker — Sample Sheet",
      "author": "Admin",
      "date": "2026-06-21",
      "category": "General",
      "tags": [
        "#BOM_Status"
      ],
      "coverImage": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/material-tracker-cover.png",
      "excerpt": "Download this sample sheet to plan BOM, PR, PO and material receipt dates before entering them into the Material Procurement Tracker.",
      "content": "<div style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Geneva,Verdana,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0\">\n\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;border-bottom:3px solid #0078d4;padding-bottom:20px;margin-bottom:30px\">\n    <h1 style=\"color:#60a5fa;margin:0\">Material BOM Tracker — Sample Sheet</h1>\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8\"><strong>Use this template to plan procurement before entering data into the tracker app</strong></p>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>\n    Getting PLC, HMI, Servo, and other critical materials on time is essential to completing\n    a project on schedule. This sheet helps you plan out <strong>BOM, PR, PO, and Material Receipt</strong>\n    dates for every item before logging them into the\n    <a href=\"/material-tracker\" style=\"color:#60a5fa\">Material Procurement Tracker</a>.\n  </p>\n\n  <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding-left:15px\">What's in the sheet</h2>\n  <ul style=\"color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>12 sample materials (PLC, HMI, Servo Drive/Motor, Safety Relay, E-Stop, etc.)</li>\n    <li>Columns for BOM Created, PR Created, PR Approved, PO Created, PO Approved, Target Receipt, Actual Receipt</li>\n    <li>A second \"Instructions\" tab explaining the date format and alert rules</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#1e3a5f;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding:20px;margin:25px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n    <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;margin-top:0\">Automatic Alert Rules in the Tracker</h2>\n    <ul style=\"color:#cbd5e1;line-height:2\">\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#ef4444\">Red flag</strong> — PR Created not filled within 3 days of BOM Created date</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#ef4444\">Red flag</strong> — PO Created not filled within 3 days of PR Approved date</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#ef4444\">Red flag</strong> — Target Receipt date passed without Actual Receipt logged</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#f59e0b\">Amber</strong> — Material due within 3 days of Target Receipt</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding-left:15px\">How to use it</h2>\n  <ol style=\"color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.8\">\n    <li>Download the sheet below</li>\n    <li>Fill in your project's material list and dates (YYYY-MM-DD format)</li>\n    <li>Open the <a href=\"/material-tracker\" style=\"color:#60a5fa\">Material Procurement Tracker</a> page</li>\n    <li>Select or add your project, paste the BOM file's link into \"BOM Location\"</li>\n    <li>Manually add each material into the tracker with its dates — the tracker will flag any item that's overdue automatically</li>\n  </ol>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:40px 0\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/raw/main/Material_BOM_Tracker_Sample.xlsx\"\n       target=\"_blank\"\n       style=\"display:inline-block;background:#16a34a;color:white;padding:14px 28px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px\">\n      📥 Download Sample BOM Tracker Sheet\n    </a>\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;margin-top:8px\">\n      Opens Excel file directly from GitHub\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:40px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px\">\n    <p>Industrial Automation Controls Team • Material Procurement Tracking</p>\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "isPublished": true,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-21T08:05:00.720Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "post-1781363231646",
      "title": "Push Button and Indicators Detail Form",
      "author": "Admin",
      "date": "2026-06-13",
      "category": "Project Update",
      "tags": [
        "#PB",
        "#Indicators"
      ],
      "coverImage": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/push-button-cover.png",
      "excerpt": "Download this form ,fill details and send it to Electrical and Mechanical Designer. In case of any input needed from Customer, share the form with your manager and get the details.",
      "content": "<div style=\"font-family:'Segoe UI',Tahoma,Geneva,Verdana,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0\">\n\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;border-bottom:3px solid #0078d4;padding-bottom:20px;margin-bottom:30px\">\n    <h1 style=\"color:#60a5fa;margin:0\">Push Buttons, Indicators & Tower Lamps</h1>\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8\"><strong>Requirement Form — Special Purpose Machines (SPM)</strong></p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding-left:15px\">Project Information</h2>\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0\">\n    <tr><th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155;text-align:left\">Field</th>\n        <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155;text-align:left\">Details</th></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Project Name</td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Project Number</td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Customer Name</td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Site Location</td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Date</td><td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td></tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding-left:15px\">1. Push Buttons</h2>\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0\">\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Type</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Color</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Function</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Qty</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Make/Model</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Start</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#22c55e\">■</span> Green</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Machine Start / Cycle Start</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Stop</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#ef4444\">■</span> Red</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Machine Stop</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">E-Stop</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#ef4444\">■</span> Red (Mushroom)</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Emergency Stop</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Reset</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#3b82f6\">■</span> Blue</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Fault Reset</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding-left:15px\">2. Indicator Lamps</h2>\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0\">\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Indicator</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Color</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Meaning</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Qty</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Power ON</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#f8fafc\">■</span> White</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Supply healthy</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Running</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#22c55e\">■</span> Green</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Machine in cycle</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Fault</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#ef4444\">■</span> Red</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Alarm / Trip</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Warning</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#f59e0b\">■</span> Amber</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Caution / Standby</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"> </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding-left:15px\">3. Tower Lamps</h2>\n  <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0\">\n    <tr>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Layer</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Color</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Condition</th>\n      <th style=\"background:#1e40af;color:white;padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Mode (Steady/Flash)</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Top</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#ef4444\">■</span> Red</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Fault / Emergency</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Flash</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Middle</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#f59e0b\">■</span> Amber</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Warning / Idle</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Steady</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Bottom</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\"><span style=\"color:#22c55e\">■</span> Green</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Running OK</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:10px;border:1px solid #334155\">Steady</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#1e3a5f;border-left:5px solid #0078d4;padding:20px;margin:25px 0;border-radius:4px\">\n    <h2 style=\"color:#93c5fd;margin-top:0\">Best Practices — IEC 60204-1 Standard Colors</h2>\n    <ul style=\"color:#cbd5e1;line-height:2\">\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#22c55e\">Green</strong> — Start / Running / Process OK</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#ef4444\">Red</strong> — Stop / Emergency / Fault</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#f59e0b\">Yellow / Amber</strong> — Warning / Standby</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#3b82f6\">Blue</strong> — Reset / Information</li>\n      <li><strong style=\"color:#f8fafc\">White</strong> — Power ON / Idle</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:40px 0\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/raw/main/Push_Buttons_Lamps_Requirement_Form.xlsx\"\n       target=\"_blank\"\n       style=\"display:inline-block;background:#16a34a;color:white;padding:14px 28px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px\">\n      📥 Download Fillable Excel Requirement Form\n    </a>\n    <p style=\"color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;margin-top:8px\">\n      Opens Excel file directly from GitHub · make sure the file is uploaded to Controls_Team_Tracker repo\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:40px;color:#64748b;font-size:13px\">\n    <p>Industrial Automation Controls Team • Special Purpose Machines</p>\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
